<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Confirmation Email</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      .content {
        padding-top: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="header">
        <h2>Confirmation Email</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <strong>[Recipient's Name]</strong>,</p>

        <p>
          Thank you for your <strong>[registration/order/scheduling]</strong>.
          This is a confirmation for your
          <strong>[meeting/order/event]</strong>.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Date & Time:</strong> [Insert date/time] <br />
          <strong>Location/Platform:</strong> [Insert location or online link]
          <br />
          <strong>Reference No:</strong> [Insert reference number if applicable]
        </p>

        <p>
          If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at
          <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a>.
        </p>

        <p>We look forward to connecting with you!</p>

        <p>
          Best regards,<br /><strong>[Your Name]</strong><br />[Your Company]
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">&copy; 2025 [Your Company]. All rights reserved.</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
